Package org.apereo.cas.support.events.service

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CasRegisteredServiceDeletedEvent
    This is CasRegisteredServiceDeletedEvent, signaled when a service is removed from the registry.
    CasRegisteredServiceLoadedEvent
    This is CasRegisteredServiceLoadedEvent that is signaled when a registered service is loaded from the registry.
    CasRegisteredServicePreDeleteEvent
    This is CasRegisteredServicePreDeleteEvent, signaled when a service about to be removed from the registry.
    CasRegisteredServicePreSaveEvent
    This is CasRegisteredServicePreSaveEvent that is signaled when a registered service about to be saved into the registry.
    CasRegisteredServiceSavedEvent
    This is CasRegisteredServiceSavedEvent that is signaled when a registered service is saved into the CAS registry.
    CasRegisteredServicesLoadedEvent
    This is CasRegisteredServicesLoadedEvent that is signaled when registered service are loaded into the CAS registry.
    CasRegisteredServicesRefreshEvent
    This is CasRegisteredServicesRefreshEvent that is signaled when a registered service is saved into the CAS registry.
